  • 所有已实现的接口:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.context.ResourceLoaderAware, org.springframework.core.env.EnvironmentCapable

    public class ClassPathMapperScanner
extends org.springframework.context.annotation.ClassPathBeanDefinitionScanner
    A ClassPathBeanDefinitionScanner that registers Mappers by basePackage, annotationClass, or markerInterface. If an annotationClass and/or markerInterface is specified, only the specified types will be searched (searching for all interfaces will be disabled). This functionality was previously a private class of org.mybatis.spring.mapper.MapperScannerConfigurer, but was broken out in version 1.2.0.
    从以下版本开始:
